General warm-up

Tabata round 2

  • Out and in jacks

Tabata round 3

  • 4 mountain climbers, 2 jacks
  • Inclined push ups

  • Skater taps

  • Wide in and out abs
  • Plie squat

Tabata round 6

  • High knees
  • Switching push up

Tabata round 7

  • Lunge twist jump
  • Plank variation

Tabata round 8

  • Side jumping ropes
  • Scissor legs

Cool down

  • Stretching
